      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·臣工之什·009.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">有客.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>有客有客，亦白其馬。有萋有且，敦琢其旅。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The noble visitor! The noble visitor!
Drawn, like his ancestors, by white horses!
The reverent and dignified,
Polished members of his suite!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-chengong-009__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
